    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in CPB use. The Claim and Requirement documentation specifies the intended use scope (Class II CPB device, 3–7 L/min, 2000–4500 RPM, 37°C blood analogue); the assessment team accepts the overall credibility package as supporting the regulatory submission decision.",
